SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(PLAN_DATE) as time_sec,
  AMOUNT as value,
  MODEL_ID as metric
FROM t_product_plan
WHERE $__timeFilter(PLAN_DATE)
ORDER BY PLAN_DATE ASC

SELECT
  s AS time_sec,
  -50.0 as value,
  'MIN' as metric
FROM (
    SELECT $__timeFrom() AS s, $__timeTo() AS e
) AS T
